author: starwarsgeek101_
title: Not so good
review: This is a good set if you are collecting football (soccer) lego products. If You do not have any soccer sets yet than don't buy this set. It really is useless. So do a favor and don't consider this set to anyone. They'll hate you if you do that! Th only thing that I consider "good" about this set is that if you are totally bored or if your kids are, and you are driving for a couple hours than this will keep you (o your kids) kind of amused for the trip. But this is definetly not my type of set.
